{"tid":1923221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當武肺影響到體育賽事 就係國際文宣最好時機","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T03:27:38.000Z","uid":306554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7bad5c5ca87e4bb53b488f08332229cb549ebe5","tid":1923221,"uid":306554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"好多外國人都對武漢肺炎不以為然，但當疫情影響到佢哋連NBA 足球都冇得睇，佢哋先會開始關注件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其好多外國人信支衛，以為中國冇隱瞞到疫情，甚至部分人比五毛網軍spin到感謝中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣依家最有用，要spin返責任去支國，係支國搞到佢地乜都冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣可以由最貼近外國文化memes 做起，例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pa29787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpa29787.jpg&h=574f78ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1rCxBe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1rCxBe.jpg&h=94a9ce9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦可以參考呢個post<br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎全球攬炒twitter文宣戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fgovhS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fgovhS</a>"},{"pid":"e500d8c1f518e4103881640969291048810190b0","tid":1923221,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"無撚有錯<br />\n中国打個乞嗤 世界真係震"},{"pid":"1dfe849c9e40dea8a5aa9b9243c51560be346252","tid":1923221,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458d532753b0ff3568547b0173cdc3488d8842c6","tid":1923221,"uid":306554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass